(<a href="http://smf.halabalooza.orgy/index.php/topic,3378.msg908462.html#msg908462" class="bbc_link">Volver al índice</a>)<br /><div align="center"><span style="font-size: 18pt;" class="bbc_size"><span style="font-family: times new roman;" class="bbc_font"><strong>7. <em>Plantillas con Blade</em></strong></span></span><br />(<a href="https://styde.net/blade-el-sistema-de-plantillas-de-laravel/" class="bbc_link new_win" target="_blank">https://styde.net/blade-el-sistema-de-plantillas-de-laravel/</a>)</div><br />Para imprimir datos con Blade:<br /><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><span style="font-family: courier;" class="bbc_font">{{ $dato }}</span></span> equivale a <span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><span style="font-family: courier;" class="bbc_font">&lt;?= e($dato) ?&gt;</span></span><br /><br />Directivas:<br /><br />La directiva foreach:<br /><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><span style="font-family: courier;" class="bbc_font">@foreach ($items as $item)<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;li&gt;{{ $item }}&lt;/li&gt;<br />@endforeach</span></span><br /><br />equivale a:<br /><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><span style="font-family: courier;" class="bbc_font">&lt;?php foreach ($items as $item): ?&gt;<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;li&gt;{{ $item }}&lt;/li&gt;<br />&lt;?php endforeach ?&gt;</span></span><br /><br />La directiva if:<br /><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><span style="font-family: courier;" class="bbc_font">@if (! empty($users))<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; ...<br />@endif</span></span><br /><br />equivale a:<br /><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><span style="font-family: courier;" class="bbc_font">&lt;?php if (! empty($users)): ?&gt;<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; ...<br />&lt;?php endif ?&gt;</span></span><br /><br />Nota: Laravel crea cache de las vistas en storage/framework/views, de tal modo que no necesitas ejecutar la función e() cada vez que se carga la página.<br /><br />Para limpiar cache desde cónsola:<br /><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><span style="font-family: courier;" class="bbc_font">&gt; art view:clear</span></span><br /><br />Ejemplo de cómo mostrar usuarios solo si hay usuarios que mostrar:<br /><br />En UserController:<br /><div class="codeheader">Código: <a href="javascript:void(0);" onclick="return smfSelectText(this);" class="codeoperation">[Seleccionar]</a></div><code class="bbc_code">public function index()<br />{<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;if (request()-&gt;has(&#039;empty&#039;)) {<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$users = &#91;];<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;} else {<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$users = [<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#039;User1&#039;, &#039;User2&#039;, &#039;User3&#039;, &#039;User4&#039;<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;];<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$title = &#039;Listado de usuarios&#039;;<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;return view(&#039;users&#039;, compact(&#039;title&#039;, &#039;users&#039;));<br />}<br /></code><br />Esta linea <span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><span style="font-family: courier;" class="bbc_font">if (request()-&gt;has(&#039;empty&#039;))</span></span> sólo sirve para verificar si hay un campo empty en &quot;get&quot;.<br />Ejemplo: <em>mi.página/usuarios?empty</em> contiene &#039;empty&#039; y validará el anterior condicional.<br /><br />En la vista users.blade.php:<br /><div class="codeheader">Código: <a href="javascript:void(0);" onclick="return smfSelectText(this);" class="codeoperation">[Seleccionar]</a></div><code class="bbc_code">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;@if (! empty($users) )<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;ul&gt;<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;@foreach ($users as $user)<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;li&gt;{{ $user }}&lt;/li&gt;<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;@endforeach<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;/ul&gt;<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;@else<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;p&gt;No hay usuarios registrados.&lt;/p&gt;<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;@endif<br /></code><br />la directiva unless (funciona a la inversa de if)<br /><div class="codeheader">Código: <a href="javascript:void(0);" onclick="return smfSelectText(this);" class="codeoperation">[Seleccionar]</a></div><code class="bbc_code">@unless($a == 0)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;// sería lo mismo que escribir @if($a != 0)<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;...<br />@else<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;...<br />@endif&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;// también se puede usar @endunless<br /></code><br />la directiva empty<br /><div class="codeheader">Código: <a href="javascript:void(0);" onclick="return smfSelectText(this);" class="codeoperation">[Seleccionar]</a></div><code class="bbc_code">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;@empty($users)<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;p&gt;No hay usuarios registrados.&lt;/p&gt;<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;@else<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;ul&gt;<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;@foreach ($users as $user)<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;li&gt;{{ $user }}&lt;/li&gt;<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;@endforeach<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;/ul&gt;<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;@endempty<br /></code><br />la directiva forelse<br /><div class="codeheader">Código: <a href="javascript:void(0);" onclick="return smfSelectText(this);" class="codeoperation">[Seleccionar]</a></div><code class="bbc_code">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;@forelse ($users as $user)<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;ul&gt;<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;@foreach ($users as $user)<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;li&gt;{{ $user }}&lt;/li&gt;<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;@endforeach<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;/ul&gt;<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;@empty<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;p&gt;No hay usuarios registrados.&lt;/p&gt;<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;@endforelse<br /></code>
